### Context

This is a Clean dataset.
The Updated New TMDB dataset contains 9193 rows and 7's columns.
The Updated TMDB dataset launched on 10/7/2021.


### Content

Contains observations of 9k+ movies like id, title, overview, release_date, popularity, vote_average, vote_count.


### Acknowledgements

This dataset was generated from The Movie Database API. This product uses the TMDb API but is not endorsed or certified by TMDb.
Their API also provides access to data on many additional movies, actors and actresses, crew members, and TV shows. You can try it for yourself here is the link https://www.themoviedb.org/documentation/api.


### Inspiration

Please Perform the best recommendation system for this new TMDB dataset.
